<caption> Pulley block arrangement </caption>
</figure>


</para>
<para id="element-166">
(a)	The force “F” is 40 N.
</para>
<para id="element-167">
(b)	The acceleration of block A is 4 
<m:math>
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mi>m</m:mi>
    <m:mo>/</m:mo>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>s</m:mi>
      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>

.
</para>
<para id="element-168">
(c) The acceleration of pulley is 1 <m:math>
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mi>m</m:mi>
    <m:mo>/</m:mo>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>s</m:mi>
      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>

</para>
<para id="element-169">
(d)The tension in the string is 10 N.

